{
  "stem": "22869.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, they were going nuts in the-- here in the middle there in the front lines.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And their commandant is yelling, and they're getting radio messages that they-- we cannot stay there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You know, we're being shot at.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The-- the war wasn't the-- the end till-- until, I think, the ninth of May.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So eventually, they took us, and they detailed us to some guys in the field who had little tents there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They let us sleep there, and they gave us some food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- we're breathing-- we're free, we're really free.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, you know, you try to touch with your hand to feel the air.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All of a sudden that-- that-- that-- that a dream like this came true.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You really-- there's no SS to shoot at you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I was sitting with a-- with a couple of guys, with Americans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And a friend of mine who I befriended on the train-- he was in the French Foreign Legion.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was much older than I am.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this guy spoke Spanish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "No, he spoke French.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he found one of the soldiers also spoke French.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So somehow they took us in in the tent there, and we stayed there about 24 hours with them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, and they were playing host to us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They was giving us whatever you want, cigarette, chocolate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, they had-- this army in their-- in their front lines, they have anything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they got a phone call one day on they-- on their field telephones that we cannot stay with them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They have to get rid of us because we can get shot still by the oncoming fire from the enemy.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There's no armistice yet, so--.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they told us, I'll tell you what.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
